{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/algorithm/5-maximum-subarray/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Soobing","author":"[Soobin Bak]","siteUrl":"https://soobing.netlify.com","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"soobing/soobing.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"soobing"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"363e9bb9-beeb-51bc-96ae-4f0eaba39777","excerpt":"의지가 너무 활활🔥 leetcode의 30Day Challenge…","html":"<p>의지가 너무 활활🔥 leetcode의 30Day Challenge <a href=\"https://leetcode.com/explore/featured/card/30-day-leetcoding-challenge/528/week-1/3285/\">문제</a>를 풀어봅시다. </p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 41%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"maximum-subway\"\n        title=\"maximum-subway\"\n        src=\"/static/8e572674460162ef88124f56b86cdb2a/e5166/maximum-subway.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8e572674460162ef88124f56b86cdb2a/f93b5/maximum-subway.jpg 300w,\n/static/8e572674460162ef88124f56b86cdb2a/b4294/maximum-subway.jpg 600w,\n/static/8e572674460162ef88124f56b86cdb2a/e5166/maximum-subway.jpg 1200w,\n/static/8e572674460162ef88124f56b86cdb2a/8f12b/maximum-subway.jpg 1506w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-요약\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD\" aria-label=\"문제 요약 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 요약</h1>\n<p>가장 합이 큰 부분집합 구하기</p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-해결\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0\" aria-label=\"문제 해결 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 해결</h1>\n<p>이 문제는 다이나믹 프로그래밍으로 오른쪽 부터 모든 경우의 수를 구해보면 문제 풀이가 쉬워집니다.\n모든 경우의 수를 찾으면 다음과 같고,\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1112px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 89.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"maximum-subway-1\"\n        title=\"maximum-subway-1\"\n        src=\"/static/9bf4682a4ad8e4d29e3807ff9b026b05/3fca6/maximum-subway-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9bf4682a4ad8e4d29e3807ff9b026b05/5a46d/maximum-subway-1.png 300w,\n/static/9bf4682a4ad8e4d29e3807ff9b026b05/0a47e/maximum-subway-1.png 600w,\n/static/9bf4682a4ad8e4d29e3807ff9b026b05/3fca6/maximum-subway-1.png 1112w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1112px) 100vw, 1112px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>메모이제이션을 사용하면 모든 경우의 수를 다음과 같이 구할 수 있습니다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"maximum-subway-2\"\n        title=\"maximum-subway-2\"\n        src=\"/static/827a9ec4c0ff6b1508ba68bd7f1a1b27/c1b63/maximum-subway-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/827a9ec4c0ff6b1508ba68bd7f1a1b27/5a46d/maximum-subway-2.png 300w,\n/static/827a9ec4c0ff6b1508ba68bd7f1a1b27/0a47e/maximum-subway-2.png 600w,\n/static/827a9ec4c0ff6b1508ba68bd7f1a1b27/c1b63/maximum-subway-2.png 1200w,\n/static/827a9ec4c0ff6b1508ba68bd7f1a1b27/d61c2/maximum-subway-2.png 1800w,\n/static/827a9ec4c0ff6b1508ba68bd7f1a1b27/cac9f/maximum-subway-2.png 2207w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>항상 모든 값을 저장하고 있을 필요는 없고, 현재 값, 지난 값에서 최댓값, 여태껏 가장 최댓값(정답)을 가지고 비교를 하면 됩니다.\n그림을 참고하시고 제가 풀이한 코드를 보시면 더 쉽게 이해할 수 있습니다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 77.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"maximum-subway-3\"\n        title=\"maximum-subway-3\"\n        src=\"/static/7930f309873e1a6ce9dacfc9256ec65a/c1b63/maximum-subway-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7930f309873e1a6ce9dacfc9256ec65a/5a46d/maximum-subway-3.png 300w,\n/static/7930f309873e1a6ce9dacfc9256ec65a/0a47e/maximum-subway-3.png 600w,\n/static/7930f309873e1a6ce9dacfc9256ec65a/c1b63/maximum-subway-3.png 1200w,\n/static/7930f309873e1a6ce9dacfc9256ec65a/d7e70/maximum-subway-3.png 1286w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"1-dp\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-dp\" aria-label=\"1 dp permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1) DP</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**\n * @param {number[]} nums\n * @return {number}\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">maxSubArray</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">nums</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> maxNum <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 마지막 값으로 초기화</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> sumNum <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 마지막 값으로 초기화</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> maxNum<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">>=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> curNum <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n        sumNum <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>curNum <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> nums<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> curNum <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> sumNum<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        maxNum <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Math<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">max</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>curNum<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sumNum<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> maxNum<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>curNum<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sumNum<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> maxNum<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> maxNum<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"🚇 Maximum Subway","date":"April 04, 2020","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"src":"/static/8e572674460162ef88124f56b86cdb2a/14b42/maximum-subway.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/algorithm/5-maximum-subarray/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/4-binarytree-inorder-traversal/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🎄Binarytree Inorder Traversal","category":"algorithm","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/6-move-zeroes/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🙆‍♀️Move Zeroes","category":"algorithm","draft":false